       <h2 class="red">
        News
       </h2>
       <img alt="Two Students in a discussion" src="img/NewsImage.jpg"/>
       <p>
        The Gender Equity Council has updated the Women at Illinois brochure.
        <a href="SupportingDocs/WomenAndIllinois.pdf" target="_blank" type="application/pdf">
         View
        </a>
        the brochure.
       </p>
       <p>
        <a href="http://inclusiveillinois.illinois.edu/commitment.html" target="_blank">
         View the Campus statement of commitment to Inclusive Illinois
        </a>
       </p>
       <p>
        <a href="SupportingDocs//2018_Impact_ODEI_Report.pdf" target="_blank">
         The 2017-2018 Diversity, Equity &amp; Inclusion report
        </a>
        is a brief departure from the format of the past, which highlighted the multitude of diversity, equity and inclusion efforts from across the entire campus. This year the focus of the report is on the development of the Office of the Vice Chancellor for Diversity, Equity &amp; Inclusion. With the establishment of this office and renewed partnerships from across the entire campus, future reports will again showcase the excellent work happening in colleges and units, at the Illinois system level and across the Big Ten to achieve Inclusive Excellence at Illinois.
       </p>
