      <div class="col home-info" role="article">
       <h2 class="blue">
        Awards
       </h2>
       <img alt="Student Quad Day" src="img/EventsImage.jpg"/>
       <h2>
        Illinois earns 2018 Higher Education Excellence in Diversity Award:
       </h2>
       <p>
        <img alt="HEED Logo" src="img/studentsarminarm.png"/>
       </p>
       <p>
        Illinois is being recognized by Insight Into Diversity magazine as a recipient of their 2018 Higher Education Excellence in Diversity (HEED) Award. The HEED Award is the only national recognition honoring
        <a class="yellowlink" href="http://www.insightintodiversity.com/about-the-heed-award/2018-recipients/" target="_blank">
         colleges and universities
        </a>
        that exhibit outstanding efforts and success in the area of diversity and inclusion throughout their campuses.
        <a class="yellowlink" href="https://news.illinois.edu/view/6367/694355" target="_blank">
         View
        </a>
        the news release.
       </p>
      </div>
