    <div class="section">
     <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
       <h3>
        Our Mission
       </h3>
       <p>
        The mission of the Office for Access and Equity is to serve as a resource to 
            campus units by facilitating compliance awareness and promoting an inclusive 
            community through diversity, education, and outreach initiatives.
       </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col col33">
